      <title>暴风雨重返迪拜，阿联酋航空和迪拜航空均遭遇航班中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/emirates-flydubai-suffer-disruptions-as-storms-return-to-dubai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于迪拜的恶劣天气，阿联酋航空被迫取消了数个航班，这是这家全球最大国际航空公司的运营几周以来第二次因降雨而受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/emirates-flydubai-suffer-disruptions-as-storms-return-to-dubai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
